# 📧 Group Email Summarizer — AI Automation

An AI-powered dashboard that reads Gmail group email threads and produces a clean summary with action items, owners, follow-up dates, and topic insights.

**Stack:** Python · Gmail API · Google Gemini · Streamlit

---

## 🗂️ Project Structure

```
email-summarizer-ai/
│
├── app.py                   ← Main pipeline (run this first)
├── requirements.txt         ← Python dependencies
│
├── config/
│   └── config.py            ← API keys and settings
│
├── services/
│   ├── email_reader.py      ← Gmail API: connect + fetch threads
│   ├── summarizer.py        ← Gemini AI: summarize thread
│   └── extractor.py         ← Gemini AI: extract topic/actions/owner
│
├── dashboard/
│   └── dashboard.py         ← Streamlit dashboard
│
├── utils/
│   └── helper.py            ← Text cleaning utilities
│
├── data/
│   └── email_summary.csv    ← Auto-generated output
│
└── README.md
```

---

## ⚙️ Setup

### 1. Install dependencies
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 2. Get Gmail API credentials
1. Go to [console.cloud.google.com](https://console.cloud.google.com)
2. Create project → Enable **Gmail API**
3. Go to **Credentials** → Create **OAuth 2.0 Client ID** (Desktop app)
4. Download JSON → rename to `credentials.json`
5. Place in the **root** of the project folder

### 3. Get Gemini API key (Free)
1. Go to [aistudio.google.com](https://aistudio.google.com)
2. Click **Get API Key** → Copy it
3. Paste into `config/config.py` → `GEMINI_API_KEY`

---

## 🚀 Running the App

### Step 1 — Run the pipeline
```bash
python app.py
```

### Step 2 — Launch the dashboard
```bash
streamlit run dashboard/dashboard.py
```

Opens at: http://localhost:8501

---

## 🔄 Workflow

```
Gmail Group Inbox
       ↓
Gmail API (email_reader.py)
       ↓
Python Processing (app.py)
       ↓
Gemini AI — Summarization (summarizer.py)
       ↓
Gemini AI — Extraction (extractor.py)
       ↓
Save to CSV (data/email_summary.csv)
       ↓
Streamlit Dashboard (dashboard.py)
```

---

## 🖥️ Dashboard Features

| Tab | Features |
|---|---|
| 📋 Summary Table | Colour-coded table: Thread, Topic, Actions, Owner, Priority |
| 🧵 Thread Details | Expandable cards per thread with full analysis |
| 📊 Insights | Priority chart · Owner chart · Top tags · Pending follow-ups |

